{"tid":838078,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【丁蟹×耀揚】5樓掟完男童掟女童落街 喪男奪2命街坊心寒","createTime":"2018-09-27T00:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T07:19:57.000Z","uid":179810,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6cff04ee9c77ec9ac0373f05e660ac5161cbcb23","tid":838078,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T00:22:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180927/58725339\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180927%2F58725339&d=fiJCY29iX%2FgwfSP31nRYpYsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=9260a2f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180927%2F58725339&h=6b2e89d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180927/58725339</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180926/large/1537965739_9435.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180926%2Flarge%2F1537965739_9435.jpg&h=41b657cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n2童命喪當場，嫌犯隨即遭到逮捕。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180926/large/1537965741_82b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180926%2Flarge%2F1537965741_82b3.jpg&h=11aedd54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n2童被從5樓（紅圈處）扔下。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n雲南安寧市2名兒童，前日（25日）傍晚從5樓接連墮樓身亡，想不到兇手竟然是42歲王姓男鄰居。由於當時正值放學時間，路上途人眾多，眾人隨即驚呼：「救命，救命！」但兩童送院後傷重死亡，王男被趕抵現場的警察拘捕。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n事發於傍晚5時34分，安寧市公安局接報，一男一女兒童被人從位於安寧市連然街道金方路一處民居扔下。警方初步調查，行兇的王姓男子是死者的鄰居，事發時潛入兩名兒童的住所，趁二人不備將他們推下窗戶，致其墮樓身亡。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n目擊者憶述，事發時只聽一聲巨響，不一會就傳出「救命！救命！」的呼喊聲。之後，樓下的清潔工發現兩名兒童躺臥在行人路上，一動也不動。附近的商戶至今仍然猶有餘悸，不敢相信居然會發生這樣的事。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n「聽說是一對男女因為欠債吵架，等聽到喊聲後趕出來看時，兩名孩子已被扔了下來。」該商戶稱，事發時間正值學校放學，道路上的行人也比較多。開始是聽到有清潔工大喊，以為是樓上有人扔東西，不料是住在5樓的一名男子先將一男孩扔下後，又將一女孩從5樓扔下，男孩當場死亡。事發後大約10分鐘有警車趕到現場，還看到警察從5樓露台的窗戶上往下看。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n目前，王男已被公安機關刑事拘留，案件有待進一步調查。至於為何他要如此兇殘扔孩童下樓，之前有傳言是因為債務問題，但警方駁斥表示「男女因欠債吵架將兩孩子扔下樓」的說法不實，目前案件詳情還在進行調查。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n雲南《都市時報》<br />\r\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i2.hoopchina.com.cn/blogfile/201012/21/129294602180282.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi2.hoopchina.com.cn%2Fblogfile%2F201012%2F21%2F129294602180282.jpg&h=68b6ba31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/07/060150_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F07%2F060150_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=fdfa74f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b0fa1c5886ec4b1a2cf6ea4c9a30e4506ce0c721","tid":838078,"uid":21782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T00:49:46.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ceaa89f5e7943010ba86788351374ff49801f7","tid":838078,"uid":56999,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T01:03:49.000Z","msg":"如果中國人人都係咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港有救了"},{"pid":"935e757c78f84de80daee273fd7599b4f6d05ee5","tid":838078,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51ceaa89f5e7943010ba86788351374ff49801f7","tid":838078,"uid":56999,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T01:03:49.000Z","msg":"如果中國人人都係咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港有救了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T06:38:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9effd1754f3bf1db1b42f43a8a5a15d203ef18e","tid":838078,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T06:41:25.000Z","msg":"屌，有聲有畫面"},{"pid":"6bddbda463207f67731634f0030a7b52debed66a","tid":838078,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T07:19:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif